high_descs: Turn right and walk into the dining room and turn left to reach the left side of the diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Move to the table to face the bread.
Cut the bread into slices with the knife.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn right to face the diningtable.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn around and head to the fridge.
Cool the slice of bread in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to reach the right side of the diningtable.
Put the bread slice on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold slice of Bread on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Go to a tall lamp in front of you, then head right, enter a room right in front, and move to the short side of a diningtable there.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Move a tiny bit to the left.
Cut the bread on the table with the knife.
Turn around and move a to a microwave on your right side.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and walk back to the diningtable.
Pick up the bread from the table.
Turn around and approach the fridge on your left.
Put the bread slice in the fridge, cool it up for a bit, then take it out.
Move to the long side of the diningtable.
Put the bread slice on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated-up bread on the diningtable.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen in front of the diningtable.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Take knife and cut some bread on top of the table.
Take the bread knife and turn around.
Walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the knife inside.
Close microwave and walk to diningtable.
Pick up a piece of bread from the table.
Walk with the piece of bread to the fridge.
Open refrigerator door and put a piece of bread on the shelf, close refrigerator door.
Take the piece of bread from the diningtable.
Walk to the diningtable and put the piece of bread on top of the table.
anns.task_desc: Get piece of bread from the refrigerator to the diningtable
